{"tid":2234349,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"北約秘書長：北約需發展新戰略思想　應對新科技及中國威脅","createTime":"2020-10-07T23:41:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T23:44:40.000Z","uid":204533,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d68748c2928710e8fa9686443c867f086e02c54b","tid":2234349,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T23:41:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>索登伯格呼籲北約30個成員國「對新科技籌謀共同原則和標準」，以應對利用大數據和網路通訊等「破壞性技術」造成的安全威脅。他又強調需要採取策略應對「中國崛起對全球力量均衡造成的根本改變」以及「更殘酷形式的恐怖主義和中東、北非的不穩定局勢」。<br />\n<br />\n在去年倫敦舉行的北約峯會上，北約成員國領袖首次確認中國構成的威脅。索登伯格說，北約在聚焦於歐洲和北美核心的同時，不可能忽略北京激增的軍事投資和在地緣政治上的主張。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201008/TK6J4DQ3WZB6JHCNPTBS7ZB3SI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201008%2FTK6J4DQ3WZB6JHCNPTBS7ZB3SI%2F&d=xM4HlgsByf6UCiwKp%2FWW5LVsU2rIM%2B0kfQ6zMqXKyqM%3D&h=ee28de72\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201008%2FTK6J4DQ3WZB6JHCNPTBS7ZB3SI%2F&h=4a17b1fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201008/TK6J4DQ3WZB6JHCNPTBS7ZB3SI/</a>"},{"pid":"64e42c7a57333989d94132df8c4b7b37bc70219f","tid":2234349,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T23:44:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.france24.com/en/20201007-nato-chief-calls-for-new-strategy-on-cyber-china\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.france24.com%2Fen%2F20201007-nato-chief-calls-for-new-strategy-on-cyber-china&d=xM4HlgsByf6UCiwKp%2FWW5LVsU2rIM%2B0kfQ6zMqXKyqM%3D&h=881e678a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.france24.com/en/20201007-nato-chief-calls-for-new-strategy-on-cyber-china</a>"}]}